    "In the current setting, the internal examinations only serve as trials for the university examinations and do not determine the student's qualification per se.",
    "Hence, the motivation factors also vary.",
    "Thus, the quantum of the syllabus, timing of the examination, and motivations might have contributed to the students' relatively low scores in the current setting.",
